{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 2226658, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 430644, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "说白了，这不就是我也不知道怎么说嘛。", "timestamp": 1628351639, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2226687, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 430644, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "确实！！！", "timestamp": 1628352005, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2226693, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 430644, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "？我喜欢说“说白了”，尤其是在给弟弟妹妹们上课的时候\n高中物理老师也喜欢，这句话后面跟的内容往往很贴近本质且形象", "timestamp": 1628352042, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2226707, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 430644, "reply_to": 2226693, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 举个例子吧", "timestamp": 1628352139, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2226713, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 430644, "reply_to": 2226693, "tag": null, "text": "我是观各类社交平台有感，树洞还没纳入统计范围，挺好奇的", "timestamp": 1628352210, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2226721, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 430644, "reply_to": 2226713, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 各类社交平台不是充满了低学历用户？", "timestamp": 1628352266, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2226730, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 430644, "reply_to": 2226721, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 对啊，树洞里用“说白了”的就挺少的", "timestamp": 1628352370, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2226743, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 430644, "reply_to": 2226730, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 也是。不过树洞里边说话的习惯跟其他平台也挺不一样的", "timestamp": 1628352457, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2226780, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 430644, "reply_to": 2226707, "tag": null, "text": "愣让我想我一时也想不到，我觉得你会这么想，在某些程度上，其实是因为“说白了”“这不就是”后面跟着的往往是你对于某个事物本质的理解，这是最能暴露你无知或有知的。dz见到的人恰恰在后面暴露了自己的无知而已…\n", "timestamp": 1628352774, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2226786, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 430644, "reply_to": 2226707, "tag": null, "text": "我在说自己不熟悉的话题的时候往往不敢说“说白了”“这不就是”，但是做家教时就常说，因为这部分我已经相对理解透彻了，可以很好地去概括本质，或者生动表达", "timestamp": 1628352851, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2226792, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 430644, "reply_to": 2226780, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 不完全是吧，从“说白了”这个词本身看，后面跟着的应该是对某个事物的简化或者类比", "timestamp": 1628352929, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2226802, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 430644, "reply_to": 2226792, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: carol手速真快", "timestamp": 1628353014, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2226812, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 430644, "reply_to": 2226792, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 类比代表着你对于本质的理解，只理解细节是无法正确类比的，同样是暴露自己不懂。（我是这个意思）\n而且我觉得洞主会这么想，是因为有些人这样说话的时候总带着居高临下、自以为是的意味，和自己本身掌握的知识形成反差后就很容易导致你的反感了", "timestamp": 1628353048, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2226816, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 430644, "reply_to": 2226802, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 我也很反感这类自以为什么都知道的人哈哈哈", "timestamp": 1628353081, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2227502, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 430644, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "在讲物理之类这种场合，我会用“通俗地讲”", "timestamp": 1628368340, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 6, "pid": 430644, "reply": 15, "tag": null, "text": "我发现越是什么都不懂的人越喜欢用诸如“说白了”，“这不就是”之类的词语。。。\n", "timestamp": 1628351597, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1628368339, "url": "", "vote": {}}}